# Ultimate Formula

```text
Binary -> Unsigned:
    int(binary, 2)

Hex -> Unsigned:
    int(hex, 16)

Unsigned -> Signed:
    n - 256 if n >= 128 else n

Signed -> Unsigned:
    n + 256 if n < 0 else n

Unsigned -> Binary:
    format(n, '08b')

Unsigned -> Hex:
    hex(n)
```
